website_summaries.verdict: The best set for creating a variety of holiday cookie shapes.
pros: Stainless steel material is easy to clean
Includes a variety of small and large cutters in various holiday shapes

customer_reviews.title: Great, but Not Sturdy
customer_reviews.text: I thought for the price these were going to be like my grandmas cookie cutters... steal, strong, not easy to bend, but these are very flimsy like made from aluminum. I probably should of done more research. I just assumed for the price of $20 it would match the price. Plus, you can’t put them in the dishwasher... I wouldn’t of bought them if I knew that. They are a great size and you do get a good many. I just wanted some that would last 20 years like my grandmas.

product_meta.title: StarPack Christmas Cookie Cutters Set (18 Piece) - Favorite Holiday Shapes including Gingerbread Man, Star and Snowflake Cutter Shapes
feature_bullets: CREATE BEAUTIFUL HOLIDAY COOKIES THIS YEAR – With this fantastic set of Christmas Cookie Cutters, you will easily be able to make gorgeous Pinterest-inspired cookies for holiday gifts and cookie trays

SAFE AND HEALTHY FOR YOUR FAMILY - We use these cookie cutters ourselves and want the best for our family and yours. The simple stainless steel design is easy to clean, the folded edges are kind to hands, and the welded seam won’t come unstuck

BE INSPIRED TO LOVE HOLIDAY BAKING AGAIN - Your new set of cookie cutters will be such a pleasure to use, you’ll soon be creating trays of beautiful and delicious cookies. You’ll even receive a FREE Bonus ‘101 Cooking Tips’ PDF to get you started!

VERSATILE AND ESSENTIAL KITCHEN SET – Contains: 8 LARGE Cookie Cutters (approx 3 to 4 Inches across), and 10 SMALL Cookie Cutters (approx 2.5 inches across. Included shapes: 2 x gingerbread men, 3 x snowflakes, 2 x Christmas trees, 2 x angels, 2 x stars, 1 x reindeer, 1 x bell, 1 x stocking, 1 x heart, 1 x linzer, 1 x snowman, and 1 x candy cane cookie cutter

QUALITY YOU CAN COUNT ON, AND OUR FULL STARPACK WARRANTY – Like all StarPack products, our cookie cutters are made to last with durable, quality materials. We offer a full refund or replacement if you’re not 100% satisfied with your purchase
